{"tid":1430152,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陶傑: 甘地其實非常激進. 香港平民都未必會接受.","createTime":"2019-08-07T16:15:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T09:58:09.000Z","uid":134071,"like":218,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"c4e8a0457d9c85dc6296e09c92b1a85a7d800e97","tid":1430152,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T16:15:51.000Z","msg":"8/7光明頂<br />\n<br />\n陶傑:<br />\n- 以香港社會既標準, 甘地既抗爭手法 其實非常激進. 香港平民都未必會接受.<br />\n- 甘地既抗爭手法, 對英國政府有用, 但中共應該唔會對此屈服<br />\n- 但另一方面, 香港持續不斷既勇武抗爭, 都未能令中共屈服.<br />\n- 抗爭者要明白和接受 香港民情和局勢 跟海外其他地區既差異.<br />\n- 抗爭最重要係爭取民意和國際支持. &nbsp;美國國會都支持香港抗爭者<br />\n- 香港抗爭要繼續, 但不要再做那些可能流失民意既行徑. &nbsp;好似 放火, 掟警署, 攻擊紀律部隊宿舍, 塞港鐵 呢D行為, 就請不要再做.<br />\n<br />\n- 建制派應舉行記者會集體支持林鄭月娥. &nbsp;所有參加今年區議會選舉既建制派代表, 都要集體出席記者會, 公開支持林鄭月娥!"},{"pid":"b12120430d21e02f0fa732166e2e8e4f07628ff0","tid":1430152,"uid":2562,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T16:16:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hmQcRzv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhmQcRzv.jpg&h=7f5efe94&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s8rvDew.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs8rvDew.jpg&h=671c6067&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RAYFf1c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRAYFf1c.jpg&h=d7384709&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1a8dc2eb7f86ec86c5a4efdf4de6275fe0a16d0d","tid":1430152,"uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T16:16:50.000Z","msg":"參考<br />\n<br />\n參考返聖雄甘地，如果要採用非勇武不合作運動，香港人重有好多野未做？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1243939/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1243939/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"c8ce9a7af25511984515284643d8eeb058b5c1f0","tid":1430152,"uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T16:17:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{